test.name: resume feedback
test.input: Review this resume for a software engineer job.

summary.skills: Strong programming skills in various languages such as Java, Python, and C++. Experience with web development, database management, and software testing. Familiar with Agile methodology and version control systems.
summary.experience: Over 5 years of experience as a software engineer, working on various projects in different industries. Proven track record of delivering high-quality and efficient solutions. Experience in both front-end and back-end development.
summary.education: Bachelor's degree in Computer Science from a top university. Continuously learning and staying updated on new technologies and programming languages.

suggestions: Include specific examples of projects and accomplishments to showcase skills and experience.
Add any relevant certifications or additional training courses.
Consider adding a section for technical skills or tools used.
Include any leadership or teamwork experience in projects.
Tailor the resume to highlight skills and experience that align with the job description.
